Package com.flipkart.business

Interface FlipFitAdminInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
FlipFitAdminService
public interface FlipFitAdminInterface
Interface for FlipFit Admin Business Logic. This interface defines various methods related to admin operations like registering admins, approving/rejecting gyms, and viewing gym or gym owner status.
